      • popupInvoked

        boolean popupInvoked(RxTableWithAddedRecords table,
                     int recordNumber,
                     javax.swing.JMenuItem item)
        The function called when the popup menu has been invoked. The parameters give the relevant information for the listener to determine whether the menu item should be enabled or disabled.
        Parameters:
        table - Table upon which the popup menu was invoked
        recordNumber - Record number upon which the popup menu was invoked
        item - The menu item to be enabled or disabled
        Returns:
        true if the menu item is to be enabled; false otherwise.
